-----------------------------
The Tabletop Simulator save files contained in this repository (ForceOrg,
Hutber, LTC Table) are the intellectual property of their respective creators
and communities:

  - LTC (League of Tactical Commanders)
  - Hutber (Hutber 40k Competitive Maps)
